If student user;
?    Investigate if student can login to another system like Moodle/KEATs using their K-Number, if they can't then it?s likely there is an issue with their username and/or password.
?    If they can access other systems, assign the ticket to Student Professional Services.
?    If their account has been in the 'debtor' status in SITS recently then you will need to create a ticket and assign to Student Professional Services to resolve. 

If staff user;
?    Investigate if staff member can login to another system like their university email account using their K-Number, if they can't then it?s likely there is an issue with their username and/or password.
